Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离地球3800米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用新型活性隐形系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲入大气层前不被发现的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,58%
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等着我! 鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来把你变成废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把一切了结吧 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.12,0:01:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}‘30周年’
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能够做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SIS请通话…! 什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民间回路逐渐关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三、第四、第七
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.22,0:02:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通讯回路不能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自动防卫系统被强行开动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续尝试直至线路回复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第五级防卫状态?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这么盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正没办法避开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有强行突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸毁卫星轨道上的自动防卫卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁它们的碎片冲人大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧起来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就混入那些碎片里冲下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:03:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 为了不被识别出机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把操纵系统关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的程式计算出这是最佳的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然计算出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的计算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信任我的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时候和技术无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎是全靠运气的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运气也是技术的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就更加不能够信任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有生命 由心至身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是! 你是被程式设计出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信自己有感情也是虚构出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的拥有自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己想做什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能够自我思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有心 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马捷虚构出来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在活动着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看他高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他…勇很快就会来到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我已经不需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美 莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 用那种光辉照耀未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来能赶得及约会的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该是你变成灰尘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阴险的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是跟在别人背后打转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有时间跟你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总要阻碍我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由小时候起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.60,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就总是跟在我背后打转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人的屁股你也穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元旦看日出时吃的鸡肉饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我买的 但你却踢翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先出脚的…是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想翻旧帐吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我买的CTV
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在还未还给我的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你七年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己不喜欢才给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中学时的饭盒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我请了你两次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我请了你十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你计算得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学园节时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毁掉我的飞机的也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙真可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都毁掉我重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年前那时候也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后 我自己把记忆锁起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和真正的记忆交换
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在骗自己…我疯了吗…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没有事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我们经常驾驶人力飞机玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关掉引擎 乘风翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们命名为‘必杀气流上升’
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道以前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道又如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直被我骂做叛徒、卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美翁 她也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们一起瞒着我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们可怜我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学园节时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我毁掉了你造的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想试一下飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去的事 忘记它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:14:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,始终感情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌声?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于遇到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的约会对像 你别出手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的对白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌声...难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求你们 快来帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘勇’
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她连超时空号的主电脑也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她完全失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂也被莎朗控制着了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美翁! 美翁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是一个空壳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌和爱情她也已经交托给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的脑内一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么? 你怎样对美翁?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有人会分开我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物由我来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去美翁那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是和这东西战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何时候也要保护美翁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美翁在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 你一定要把她抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你不能打败鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.27,0:19:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样做或许更明智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连你也一样! 说什么…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别慢吞吞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激死! 两个人也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后别哀求我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超时空号…在开动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像记起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续接近有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收声! 正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竞争、伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心底的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你收藏起来的一切感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗把超时空号占据了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制止莎朗去破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超时空号的情报网络中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心脏部份在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇已经是我的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.02,0:22:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了! 要害在主天线后面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正下方13D
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是勇吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.74,0:23:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美翁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.87,0:23:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把病毒…输入莎朗的网络
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令她混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多余的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止! 我求你! 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有人能够阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.65,0:23:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来阻止给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.23,0:24:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.26,0:24:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.07,0:24:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你所希望的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.48,0:24:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.35,0:24:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给予这世上每一个人应有的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.52,0:25:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实现爱人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.86,0:25:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他最大的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.39,0:25:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心想‘那就是我活着的证明’
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.14,0:25:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里会有…?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.07,0:25:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么…?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种无聊的感动 到处也没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇所寻求的是遥远的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.35,0:25:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拚命挑战天空时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.32,0:25:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在生死之间
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.12,0:25:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,窥见的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.69,0:25:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想勇感到那种感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.87,0:25:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.91,0:26:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.08,0:26:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.53,0:26:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.80,0:26:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有解除限制器发挥极限性能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.24,0:26:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇 情况怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.71,0:26:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特吗? 很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.72,0:26:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到美翁了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.18,0:26:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.09,0:26:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.23,0:26:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.86,0:26:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这边很快便弄妥
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.90,0:26:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我期待跟你大打一埸
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.08,0:26:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.17,0:27:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝我们七年后久别重逢 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.94,0:27:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 我先行一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.28,0:27:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.72,0:27:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特…加鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.09,0:27:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘危险极点’
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.07,0:27:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.25,0:27:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快…就能…接上莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.66,0:28:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杨
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.03,0:28:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.37,0:28:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这东西连杨也
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.75,0:29:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌! 我不想听你的怪歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.37,0:29:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.41,0:29:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想听的…不是你的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.14,0:30:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个词语是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.41,0:30:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从沉睡中
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.65,0:30:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我内心的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.89,0:30:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.54,0:30:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二个词语是风
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.34,0:31:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我的前路
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.72,0:31:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‘超时空城市的鸟瞰图’
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.52,0:32:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.69,0:32:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个词语是梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从沉睡中
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.14,0:33:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我内心的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.05,0:33:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地带出来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.42,0:33:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二个词语是风
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.59,0:33:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}献给你 我们的未来拓荒者
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.16,0:33:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我的前路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.33,0:33:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摆动翅膀飞向上帝的臂弯内
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.18,0:34:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像数着已消逝的悲伤往事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.99,0:34:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金色的苹果 又有一个跌下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.91,0:34:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从未见过的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.75,0:34:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是归宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.86,0:34:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的生命到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.48,0:34:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咏唱古老的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.02,0:35:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在月色幽静的晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.36,0:35:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着将来能遇见的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.71,0:35:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU CAN FLY
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.65,0:35:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WE HAVE DREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.95,0:35:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WE CAN TOUCH
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.29,0:35:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOUR DREAMS
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.52,0:35:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONLY FLY
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.63,0:35:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SO FAR
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.83,0:35:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TO THE WIND
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.37,0:35:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,IN THE NIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.21,0:36:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三个词语是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.09,0:36:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,细意倾听的说话
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.73,0:36:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你抖震的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.10,0:36:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄地放开

